headline: KEY WEALTH RECOGNIZED WITH TWO AWARDS AT THE 2025 FAMILY WEALTH REPORT AWARDS
summary: Key Family Wealth, the multi-family office division of Key Wealth, was named "Best Family Wealth Solution" for its enhanced legacy planning services at the 2025 Family Wealth Report (FWR) awards. Cathy O'Malley Kearney, national head of Key Private Bank, was also recognized with a leadership award, 'Woman in Wealth Banking' for her leadership in the wealth management industry.
